OL,3,CMurder accused appears in court after
OL,4,Cwoman's body found at home
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering a woman whose body was
OL,8,Fdiscovered at a house in West
OL,9,FYorkshire.
OL,11,FCarolann Barraclough, 37, was found
OL,12,Fdead at the property in Ken Churchill
OL,13,FDrive, Horbury, near Wakefield, after
OL,14,Fpolice responded to reports raising
OL,15,Fconcern for her safety on Friday 6
OL,16,FMarch.
OL,18,FDavid Barraclough appeared before
OL,19,FLeeds Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,20,Fcharged with murder.
