OL,3,CMurder accused appears in court after
OL,4,Cwoman's body found at home
OL,6,FThe 45-year-old, of Ken Churchill
OL,7,FDrive, did not enter a plea during the
OL,8,Fshort hearing and was remanded into
OL,9,Fcustody ahead of an appearance at
OL,10,FLeeds Crown Court on Tuesday.
